{"about_the_game":"Dive into a unique fusion of classic RPG and deckbuilding, where epic adventures meet strategic card battles. Ascend the Tower of Legends, build your own deck, confront fearsome monsters, and forge your own destiny.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/anim.heart.decay.gif?t=1730737372\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LIFE IN THE CARDS</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/LifeInCardsUpper.gif?t=1730737372\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/LifeInCardsLower.gif?t=1730737372\" /><br><br>Health is a valuable resource in this game. Every card played exacts a toll on your health points, making every decision a high-stakes gamble. Choose your moves wisely, as you must balance power with preservation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UNIQUE DECK BUILDING</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/BuildUniqueDecksEquip.gif?t=1730737372\" /><br><br>Collect a vast array of cards during your journey, each with its own set of abilities and consequences. Your deck evolves as you progress, reflecting your character's growth and adaptability.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ALTER THE RULES</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/WorldCardsCrop.gif?t=1730737372\" /><br><br>Use world cards to change the rules of the game and raid the dungeon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VARIABLE DIFFICULTY</h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/DifficultySelectionCrop.gif?t=1730737372\" /><br><br>Ensures that the game can be played by newcomers and veterans alike.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PROCEDURALLY GENERATED FLOORS</h2>Brace yourself for an ever-changing challenge. Each floor of the Tower is procedurally generated, ensuring that no two runs are the same. Unearth hidden secrets, discover new strategies, and face unforeseen obstacles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FRESH ART STYLE</h2>Retro pixel art implemented in a 3D world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/anim.heart.decay.gif?t=1730737372\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730737372","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1730737372","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/a40da33739e8cd2f5986cea389bfe4387d903193/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730737372","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/a40da33739e8cd2f5986cea389bfe4387d903193/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730737372","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Dive into a unique fusion of classic RPG and deckbuilding, where epic adventures meet strategic card battles. Ascend the Tower of Legends, build your own deck, confront fearsome monsters, and forge your own destiny.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331480/extras/anim.heart.decay.gif?t=1730737372\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">LIFE IN THE CARDS</h2><br><img class=\"b